snippet.textDisplay: Kal jo mujhe kohinoor dene ka wada jo kar gaye, aaj haath mei kaanch ka tukda chubha gaye nahi tha to mana hi kar dete ye bhi nahi to bahega khoon tumhe maloom tha to kam se kam dwai to de jaate itna ahsaan kar dete to, sach me aapko maaf kar dete, aur socho kohinoor ki jagah 2 kohinoor de dete to hum dil se ro dete, is baat ko tum na jaane kitna yaad kar lete aapse seekh ke hum bhi 2 ki jagah kisi ko 4 kohinoor de dete, badle me sache pyaar ka ahsaan le lete socho itni badi cheej ka ahsaas aapse hua aapko kitna dil se yaad karte itne bhole hai ki aap thag gaye ye bhole hi aapko shayad khuda maan lete 🤩
